HEADWORD: Depolarizer
<hw>De*po"lar*i`zer</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Elec.)</fld>
<def>A substance used to prevent polarization, as upon the negative
plate of a voltaic battery.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

